{"tid":296898,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"黎棟國：對警員被稱「黑警」感痛心","createTime":"2017-06-25T04:17:32.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-26T16:29:47.000Z","uid":20933,"like":2,"dislike":59,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"26f356ace1a23bb8ceea158c3f17fd36c413268e","tid":296898,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-25T04:17:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/e-paper/20170625/large/1498361305_df3a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.appledaily.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170625%2Flarge%2F1498361305_df3a.jpg&h=59dd29e3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n即將卸任保安局局長一職的黎棟國出席電台節目時表示，對於在任期間發生佔領事件警方被稱為「黑警」感到痛心，他指警方盡忠職守，面對前所未有挑戰都盡心盡力處理，非常慶幸無生命損失，「如果冇記錯，受傷最嚴重係警務人員」。<br />\n<br />\n據多個民間團體2015年曾發表「雨傘運動警權報告」，推算雨傘運動期間至少2,067人身心受創。團體以9月28日至30日期間，金鐘紅十字會錄得142宗受傷個案、醫管局在運動後公佈共錄得528人入院等數據，按比例推算至少1,334人受傷，其中28人因頭部受傷入院，當中4人出現短暫神志不清或骨科瘀傷要留院觀察。<br />\n<br />\n報告又詳列多個受訪個案，清楚顯示警方驅趕人群時多次濫用武力，例如無警告下近距離使用胡椒噴霧、胡椒水劑，更有人被警員故意拳打腳踢。"},{"pid":"87c6d80cedb12ffd2d15e1d1ff8ee448d4952573","tid":296898,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-25T04:18:13.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?issue=20170625&amp;guid=56873197&amp;category_guid=6996647&amp;category=instant\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fissue%3D20170625%26guid%3D56873197%26category_guid%3D6996647%26category%3Dinstant&d=9%2BZN6Ff8PaoQpbDbzc4Ei0jIoeaDRyeQRMy%2FzT52C%2Fo%3D&h=4c3d01b0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fissue%3D20170625%26guid%3D56873197%26category_guid%3D6996647%26category%3Dinstant&h=fe3c962c\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?issue=20170625&amp;guid=56873197&amp;category_guid=6996647&amp;category=instant</a>"},{"pid":"896f8fec32db0d7143ebd71e43947b806ae91640","tid":296898,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"reply